item.title: Im going to cry....lmao help plz
item.dc:creator: @Khasck Khasck
item.description:
@Khasck wrote:

she has moparscape w/ aryan…
look at the screenies…
and like i said, i would download that 6.0 JDK.
if it still doesnt work, go to “start” and then “search” and then search for all files named moparscape.
then delete them all.
then go to moparisthebest.com, and reload them all.
this error can happen if you have two or more moparscape clients on your computer.
like, you downloaded the first one, then you deleted the client alone, and you left the file that you downloaded alone, becuase you couldnt find it, am i correct?
then same thing over again, most likely.
then you downloaded this one or maybe even more, and now it doesnt work.
if you delete all moparscape files, and redownload it onto your computer, it should work.
i hope this helps ya,

-Will
